ğŸ“ˆ Key Findings
Education ODA shows a positive correlation with literacy rate (Pearson r â‰ˆ +0.65).
Health ODA is moderately linked to life expectancy (r â‰ˆ +0.58).
Combined educationâ€“health models explain development variance better than single-sector models.
Several middle-income countries show a mismatch between high ODA inflows and slower outcome growth.

